"<pad> if we want to build models that can really learn language, then on-line learning is crucial. it does not seem that simple recurrent neural networks can capture truly long context infor- mation, as cache models still provide complementary informa- tion even to dynamic models trained with BPTT. Especially tasks inflectional languages or languages with large vocabu- lary might benefit from using NN based models, as was already shown in [12]. this work was partly supported by European project - - a</s>"